nl.tudelft.simulation.examples.dsol.terminal

Interface IntResourceRequestorInterface<A extends java.lang.Comparable<A>,R extends java.lang.Number & java.lang.Comparable<R>,T extends nl.tudelft.simulation.dsol.simtime.SimTime<A,R,T>>

  • Type Parameters:
    A - the absolute time type to use in timed events
    R - the relative time type
    T - the simulation time type.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Container

    public interface IntResourceRequestorInterface<A extends java.lang.Comparable<A>,R extends java.lang.Number & java.lang.Comparable<R>,T extends nl.tudelft.simulation.dsol.simtime.SimTime<A,R,T>>
    This interface provides a callback method to the resource. Whenever resource is available this method is invoked on the requestor.
